Mapping between the database and the XML

Book
id: node=pgterms:ebook attribute=rdf:about "ebooks/45213"
title: node=dcterms:title 1st line
subtitle: node=dcterms:title 2nd-last lines
language: node=dcterms:language/rdf:Description/rdf:value
downloads: node=pgterms:downloads

Author:
gut_id: node=dcterms:creator/pgterms:agent attribute=rdf:about "2009/agents/216"
